<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Happy Birthday My Love</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e 0%, #fecfef 99%, #feada6 100%);
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            color: #4a4a4a;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .card-container {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 35px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.3);
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #ffb6c1;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #d63384;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-family: 'Brush Script MT', cursive, serif;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #e63946;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .image-gallery {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .image-gallery img {
            width: 31%;
            min-width: 160px;
            height: 180px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .image-gallery img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .wish-message {
            font-size: 1.05em;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #333;
            text-align: justify;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #d63384;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .romantic-quotes {
            background: #fff0f5;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff69b4;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .romantic-quotes p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            color: #c2185b;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .footer-hugs {
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #e63946;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .image-gallery img {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="card-container">
        <h1>Happy Birthday, My Passionate Love! 💕</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">To the one who sets my heart on fire...</div>

        <!-- Image Gallery with Online Romance, Cake, and Hug Images -->
        <div class="image-gallery">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518199266791-5375a83190b7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Romantic Sunset Couple Hug">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1535141192574-5d4897c13136?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Delicious Birthday Cake">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516589178581-6cd7833ae3b2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Couple Warm Warm Hug">
        </div>

        <!-- Birthday Wish Content (approx 220 words) -->
        <div class="wish-message">
            Happy Birthday to the one who holds my heart, my soul, and my deepest desires. Today, as we celebrate the incredible day you were born, I want to wrap my arms tightly around you, pull you close, and never let go. Every single moment spent with you feels like a beautiful dream filled with intense warmth, passion, and endless joy. Your touch electrifies me, your soft smile melts away all my worries, and your presence fills my world with vibrant colors of romance.
            <br><br>
            On this special day, I wish you a year ahead overflowing with sweetness, magical memories, and boundless love. May your day be as intoxicatingly marvelous as you are to me. I am sending you endless warm hugs, tender kisses, and all the passionate affection my heart can possibly hold. Thank you for being my soulmate, my lover, and my favorite person to embrace forever. 💖✨
        </div>

        <!-- Romantic Text Messages at the End -->
        <div class="romantic-quotes">
            <p>💋 "In your arms is my favorite place to be, tonight and for eternity."</p>
            <p>🔥 "You aren't just my love—you are my sweetest addiction."</p>
            <p>🌹 "Happy Birthday, sweetheart! I can't wait to shower you with warm hugs and endless kisses today."</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-hugs">
            🤗 Sweeter Than Cake, Warmer Than Hugs! 🤗
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
